data.description: Come see this beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bath home located in the desirable neighborhood of Fox Ridge, in Cooper ISD. This home is preloved but has all the updated features one would want! Built by Edge Homes in 2019. Right when you walk in, you'll be greeted with vaulted ceiling and a beautiful staircase leading to 2 bedrooms. The living room has a fireplace with stone that goes all the way to the ceiling and is open to the kitchen/dining room. As you go through the laundry room it leads you to the primary room. One would only want the custom bathroom details which has a double vanity, and a true walk-in closet. The shed in the back is off to the side so no grass space was taken from your entertaining needs. ENJOY the covered patio and make this home yours today!
